gerin Elfriede Jelinek und dem „Verweigerungskünstler“ Thomas Bernhard wurde den Verbindungslinien beider Autoren noch nie vergleichend nachgegangen. Der Band erschließt zum 30. Todestag Bernhards (u. 15 Jahre Nobelpreis für Jelinek) anschaulich ein breit gefächertes Spektrum an Themen, Perspektiven und Werken beider Schriftsteller im Vergleich. Mit einem Essay von Elfriede Jelinek.  aWhile there are countless studies of both Nobel Prize winning writer Elfriede Jelinek and “refusal artist” Thomas Bernhard, the connections between the two authors have never been studied in a comparative key. On the occasion of the 30th anniversary of Bernhard’s death, this volume offers an accessible comparative examination of a broad range of topics, perspectives, and works by both writers. With an essay by Elfriede Jelinek.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aBernhard, Thomas. 4aJelinek, Elfriede. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aBernhard, Thomas.  aJelinek, Elfriede.1 aBozzi, Paola, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaduff, Corina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEgel, Antonia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGschwandtner, Harald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGötze, Clemens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGötze, Clemens, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aJelinek, Elfriede, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJudex, Bernhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJurgensen, Manfred, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlenner, Jens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeis, Veren